Kennedy Osei (amụrụ na 21 Ọktoba na afọ 1966) bụ onye Ghana na-agba ọsọ n'etiti etiti nke lara ezumike nká nke bụ ọkachamara na mita 800.
O meriri ọla nchara na 1991 All-Africa Games. O mekwara asọmupi na World Championships na afọ 1993 na afọ1997 yana World Indoor Championships na 1993, na-eru na ọkara ikpeazụ n'oge ọ bụla.
